text: Lee Seo-el is a South Korean actress and model. She is best known for her roles in dramas such as Rugal and Born Again. ==Biography and career== Lee Seo-el is a South Korean model and actress. She was a model then she made her first acting debut in 2020 when she took on her first role in the television drama Rugal which attracted attention to her role as Yeo-jin and in the same year she was cast in drama Born Again as Baek Sang-ah. ==Filmography== ===Television series=== {| class="wikitable" |- !
